1
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:58,229
His Majesty has arrived.

2
00:01:59,590 --> 00:02:01,200
Your Majesty, you're late.

3
00:02:04,870 --> 00:02:06,280
I was busy checking

4
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:08,000
the treasury ledger you gave me.

5
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,840
There were too many accounting records.

6
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:11,000
I haven't finished checking them today.

7
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:11,710
That's why

8
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:12,870
I'm late.

9
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:16,540
Your Highness.

10
00:02:18,079 --> 00:02:20,140
Xiao Chi has been keeping me company.

11
00:02:20,150 --> 00:02:21,400
We all

12
00:02:22,030 --> 00:02:23,870
grew up under your watchful eye.

13
00:02:24,750 --> 00:02:27,400
So, I brought him along.

14
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,240
Good.

15
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:33,170
It's been a while since we drank together.

16
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,940
A toast to Your Majesty first.

17
00:02:36,470 --> 00:02:37,520
I haven't

18
00:02:37,910 --> 00:02:39,280
shared a drink with you

19
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,740
in a long time either, Xie.

20
00:02:41,470 --> 00:02:41,870
Then,

21
00:02:41,870 --> 00:02:43,079
today can be considered a family reunion

22
00:02:43,079 --> 00:02:44,680
for us.

23
00:02:45,430 --> 00:02:46,240
Let me

24
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,460
toast to our father first.

25
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,150
What?

26
00:03:06,030 --> 00:03:08,030
Are you afraid that I'll poison you?

27
00:03:09,030 --> 00:03:10,000
Of course, not.

28
00:03:10,630 --> 00:03:11,870
Let us

29
00:03:12,030 --> 00:03:13,490
share this bottle of wine.

30
00:03:13,630 --> 00:03:14,190
Okay.

31
00:03:15,150 --> 00:03:16,030
Then,

32
00:03:16,630 --> 00:03:18,150
thank you, Xie.

33
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,190
This is

34
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,560
to our Liu Empire.

35
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,280
To our

36
00:03:32,079 --> 00:03:33,470
sibling bond.

37
00:03:46,190 --> 00:03:47,190
Your Highness.

38
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,410
Don't wait anymore.

39
00:03:48,470 --> 00:03:51,670
His Majesty went to
the Eldest Princess' palace tonight.

40
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,810
I didn't expect him to come.

41
00:03:57,430 --> 00:03:59,430
I just have a bad premonition.

42
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:03,030
Xie, you asked me here

43
00:04:03,030 --> 00:04:04,590
for more than just drinking, right?

44
00:04:04,590 --> 00:04:05,400
What else?

45
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:08,210
You are usually straightforward.

46
00:04:08,470 --> 00:04:09,630
Why do you seem

47
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:11,840
strange today?

48
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,070
Since then,

49
00:04:16,430 --> 00:04:18,000
I will be frank.

50
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:20,630
Liu Chu.

51
00:04:22,070 --> 00:04:23,750
You murdered important ministers,

52
00:04:23,750 --> 00:04:25,160
destabilizing the court,

53
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:26,600
bringing down a toxic plague,

54
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,260
and making the people suffer.

55
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,600
You held a grand marriage
alliance ceremony

56
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,800
that emptied the treasury.

57
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:33,530
You have accomplished
nothing in state affairs.

58
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:35,860
You are not fit to be
the ruler of Jinglan.

59
00:04:35,870 --> 00:04:37,000
I'm not fit?

60
00:04:37,630 --> 00:04:38,430
Xie.

61
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:40,390
I am our father's only son.

62
00:04:40,390 --> 00:04:41,270
If I'm not fit,

63
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,310
are you?

64
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:44,920
A son?

65
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:47,430
If I were the ruler,

66
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:50,070
I would expand the territory

67
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:52,159
and let the people live in peace.

68
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:54,190
Women are not inferior to men.

69
00:05:00,190 --> 00:05:02,390
If you took the throne,

70
00:05:03,070 --> 00:05:04,430
after you pass away,

71
00:05:05,270 --> 00:05:07,360
who would you pass it to?

72
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,070
To an outsider?

73
00:05:09,070 --> 00:05:10,270
Don't worry about that.

74
00:05:10,270 --> 00:05:12,240
I will let Consort Ling's child

75
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,370
inherit the throne.

76
00:05:13,830 --> 00:05:16,870
This empire will always
belong to the Liu Family.

77
00:05:17,070 --> 00:05:19,190
Then, how do you plan to deal with me?

78
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,270
I hope

79
00:05:22,190 --> 00:05:24,360
you can stay
in the Princess's Mansion.

80
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,960
Eat and drink well every day.

81
00:05:26,270 --> 00:05:28,040
I will provide for you until you die.

82
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:29,480
I think this is

83
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:31,140
the best choice for both of us.

84
00:05:32,270 --> 00:05:33,190
But what if

85
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,600
I refuse?

86
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:37,190
You

87
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:38,600
have to.

88
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,360
Xie,

89
00:05:43,870 --> 00:05:45,390
this is treason.

90
00:05:46,950 --> 00:05:48,190
You forced me.

91
00:05:48,870 --> 00:05:50,040
Guards!

92
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:54,960
Your Majesty!

93
00:06:21,630 --> 00:06:23,160
Surrender now.

94
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:26,240
Then, you and Xiao Chi can survive.

95
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,040
Think about

96
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:29,040
your so-called good brothers.

97
00:06:51,270 --> 00:06:52,190
Fei Zheng?

98
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,390
I didn't expect your swordsmanship

99
00:06:53,390 --> 00:06:54,600
to be so excellent.

100
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,070
Greetings, Your Highness.

101
00:06:56,070 --> 00:06:57,390
Now, you three brothers

102
00:06:57,390 --> 00:06:58,480
are all here.

103
00:06:58,830 --> 00:06:59,480
Kill them!

104
00:07:12,950 --> 00:07:13,750
Stop!

105
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:15,360
The Eldest Princess of the royal family

106
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,890
cannot be killed so easily.

107
00:07:17,950 --> 00:07:18,800
It is not

108
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:21,680
the time to kill her.

109
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:32,950
Eldest Princess Liu Xie

110
00:07:33,159 --> 00:07:35,000
has secretly formed cliques

111
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:36,830
and plotted treason.

112
00:07:36,870 --> 00:07:39,070
I feel heartbroken about that.

113
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,070
Today,

114
00:07:40,390 --> 00:07:42,070
I'll strip her of her title

115
00:07:42,070 --> 00:07:44,240
and confine her to the Princess's Mansion.

116
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:46,560
She shall not leave unless in death.

117
00:07:46,830 --> 00:07:48,830
By Imperial Command.

118
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,480
Guards!

119
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,830
Guards!

120
00:08:39,270 --> 00:08:40,750
Come to see me!

121
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:43,960
Liu Chu!

122
00:08:44,390 --> 00:08:45,480
You coward!

123
00:08:45,550 --> 00:08:47,080
Are you afraid to see me?

124
00:08:48,550 --> 00:08:49,840
Liu Chu!

125
00:09:04,030 --> 00:09:04,910
Father,

126
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:08,440
why are you doing this to me?

127
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:20,790
Zheng knows martial arts?

128
00:09:21,390 --> 00:09:23,440
And he used Changmo's swordplay?

129
00:09:37,270 --> 00:09:38,870
How could you be so careless?

130
00:09:40,390 --> 00:09:41,190
It's nothing.

131
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:49,940
Something's on your mind.

132
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:53,000
I just feel that

133
00:09:53,510 --> 00:09:54,910
people are complicated,

134
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:56,880
and human nature is cold.

135
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:58,150
But

136
00:09:58,150 --> 00:10:00,150
no matter how things change,

137
00:10:00,750 --> 00:10:03,210
we've been through
life and death together.

138
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:04,630
Yeah.

139
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:07,750
We've been through
life and death together.

140
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:08,600
After all,

141
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:12,140
we've experienced so much together.

142
00:10:13,150 --> 00:10:14,080
How about

143
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:15,270
I have a drink with you?

144
00:10:15,270 --> 00:10:16,480
Then,

145
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:18,150
I'll suffer a lot.

146
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:19,550
Don't worry.

147
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,480
I have a hangover cure.

148
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,200
But your hangover cure...

149
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:24,460
I changed its formula.

150
00:10:52,270 --> 00:10:53,510
In the past,

151
00:10:54,270 --> 00:10:55,750
I liked this place the most.

152
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:56,810
I enjoyed drinking

153
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:58,560
and moon gazing here.

154
00:10:59,550 --> 00:11:00,880
It has a special flavor.

155
00:11:03,670 --> 00:11:04,480
I know.

156
00:11:05,550 --> 00:11:07,000
Occasional freedom

157
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:08,240
can make us briefly

158
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:10,000
forget earthly troubles.

159
00:11:11,670 --> 00:11:13,270
I really like it here too,

160
00:11:13,870 --> 00:11:16,150
but drinking on the dunes in Changmo

161
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:17,840
would be even more freeing.

162
00:11:20,390 --> 00:11:22,250
If we can return to Tianlang Pass,

163
00:11:22,750 --> 00:11:24,080
you'd share a pot of wine with me

164
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,630
on the dunes.

165
00:11:26,750 --> 00:11:27,870
Don't worry.

166
00:11:28,790 --> 00:11:30,920
I'm just afraid you can't outdrink me.

167
00:11:31,630 --> 00:11:32,830
I can't outdrink you?

168
00:11:39,670 --> 00:11:40,720
Sometimes,

169
00:11:41,270 --> 00:11:43,240
I really want to go back to our childhood.

170
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:44,240
Back then,

171
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,150
Chu,

172
00:11:46,910 --> 00:11:47,670
Zheng,

173
00:11:50,080 --> 00:11:51,510
and I were the closest ones

174
00:11:51,510 --> 00:11:52,960
in this world.

175
00:11:54,750 --> 00:11:56,150
Back then, I thought that

176
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:59,800
we would be good brothers
for the rest of our lives.

177
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,600
His Majesty

178
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:03,000
still treats you very well now.

179
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,200
And so does Lord Fei.

180
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:06,840
Yes.

181
00:12:07,360 --> 00:12:08,840
They do treat me well.

182
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,480
They always have.

183
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,080
But now,

184
00:12:17,080 --> 00:12:18,480
everything has changed.

185
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:23,840
Power can change many people and things.

186
00:12:24,030 --> 00:12:26,670
But some relationships will never change.

187
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:35,440
I plan to ask Chu for permission

188
00:12:35,870 --> 00:12:38,000
to go back and guard the Tianlang Pass.

189
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:41,040
The conditions there are harsh,

190
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:43,280
but at least there are no distractions.

191
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:48,660
Do you want to come with me?

192
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,080
Did you think I couldn't bear to leave

193
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:51,680
the medical hall you gave me?

194
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:52,840
Tell you the truth.

195
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:54,670
I've wanted to go back for a long time.

196
00:12:54,670 --> 00:12:55,480
Really?

197
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:57,160
Why would I lie to you?

198
00:12:57,550 --> 00:12:58,360
Okay.

199
00:13:02,150 --> 00:13:03,810
I've been carrying this pouch

200
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:05,240
with me all the time.

201
00:13:07,750 --> 00:13:08,670
Though

202
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:11,760
this is a gift you gave me,

203
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,600
today,

204
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:15,580
I want to give it to you.

205
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:18,740
Let's go back to Tianlang Pass together.

206
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:20,960
You promised me.

207
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:27,260
Yes, I promise you.

208
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:30,000
Okay.

209
00:13:38,150 --> 00:13:40,390
My mission is almost done.

210
00:13:41,750 --> 00:13:43,750
I will depart for Changmo tomorrow.

211
00:13:44,670 --> 00:13:45,390
Then,

212
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:48,060
who will assign missions
to Fei Zheng and me?

213
00:13:48,390 --> 00:13:49,120
Let Fei Zheng

214
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:54,000
fend for himself.

215
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:55,840
Then,

216
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:56,880
what about me?

217
00:13:58,550 --> 00:14:00,120
Didn't the Princess ask you to
return to the palace

218
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:01,360
and stay by her side?

219
00:14:01,480 --> 00:14:03,240
Anyway, Liu Xie is already
under house arrest.

220
00:14:03,240 --> 00:14:04,080
You can go back

221
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:06,080
and continue waiting for my return.

222
00:14:07,030 --> 00:14:08,600
What about the Gu poison in my body?

223
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:09,550
Don't worry.

224
00:14:09,840 --> 00:14:11,700
I will leave you enough antidote.

225
00:14:16,270 --> 00:14:16,910
Remember,

226
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,600
you will always be

227
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:20,240
a killing tool of Caidie Hall.

228
00:14:20,240 --> 00:14:22,630
You can never escape the grasp of Changmo.

229
00:15:26,480 --> 00:15:27,670
This body is

230
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:31,240
getting weaker.

231
00:15:50,030 --> 00:15:51,000
Jin Xi.

232
00:15:51,750 --> 00:15:53,550
Jin Xi.

233
00:15:59,120 --> 00:16:01,450
Jin Xi hasn't come to see
me for a long time.

234
00:16:12,790 --> 00:16:13,650
Your Highness,

235
00:16:14,150 --> 00:16:15,410
are you looking for me?

236
00:16:16,480 --> 00:16:17,440
Jin Xi.

237
00:16:23,000 --> 00:16:24,000
Jin Xi,

238
00:16:24,390 --> 00:16:25,630
it is you.

239
00:16:25,630 --> 00:16:26,150
Yes.

240
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:31,000
You came to the palace to keep me company.

241
00:16:31,000 --> 00:16:31,440
Yes,

242
00:16:31,670 --> 00:16:33,400
I came back to keep you company.

243
00:16:33,870 --> 00:16:35,270
And you will never leave?

244
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:36,800
I won't leave.

245
00:16:38,790 --> 00:16:40,550
Talk with me more.

246
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:41,870
Without you,

247
00:16:42,150 --> 00:16:43,870
I have nothing to say to them.

248
00:16:45,150 --> 00:16:46,240
What's up?

249
00:16:47,150 --> 00:16:48,150
Now that I'm back,

250
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:49,390
are you not happy?

251
00:16:50,080 --> 00:16:52,390
I am happy.

252
00:16:55,080 --> 00:16:56,480
Will the Eldest Princess

253
00:16:56,550 --> 00:16:58,030
let you stay here?

254
00:17:01,240 --> 00:17:02,700
Liu Xie intended to rebel.

255
00:17:03,030 --> 00:17:04,109
She has been grounded by Liu Chu

256
00:17:04,109 --> 00:17:05,440
in the Princess Palace.

257
00:17:06,030 --> 00:17:07,069
How could she?

258
00:17:07,349 --> 00:17:08,550
The assassins she trained,

259
00:17:08,550 --> 00:17:10,000
and Lan by her side

260
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:10,880
are all dead.

261
00:17:11,270 --> 00:17:12,000
Otherwise,

262
00:17:12,200 --> 00:17:13,270
I wouldn't have been able to

263
00:17:13,270 --> 00:17:14,730
return to you so smoothly.

264
00:17:16,880 --> 00:17:18,940
How could the Eldest Princess rebel?

265
00:17:19,160 --> 00:17:20,550
I must go see her.

266
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:24,880
Don't do it right now.

267
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:26,750
We are unable to figure out

268
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:29,030
the matters between Liu Xie and Liu Chu.

269
00:17:29,030 --> 00:17:30,830
But when I came to Jinglan,

270
00:17:31,960 --> 00:17:33,350
she was so nice to me.

271
00:17:35,750 --> 00:17:37,680
If she were truly kind to you,

272
00:17:38,240 --> 00:17:39,960
she wouldn't have

273
00:17:39,960 --> 00:17:42,960
confined you to your quarters
when Liu Chu was in a coma.

274
00:17:42,960 --> 00:17:43,720
Besides,

275
00:17:44,310 --> 00:17:46,350
she wanted to kill her own brother.

276
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:48,730
How could she be sincere to you?

277
00:17:50,590 --> 00:17:52,070
Is she really that bad?

278
00:17:52,070 --> 00:17:53,400
Whether she's good or bad

279
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:55,260
has nothing to do with us anymore.

280
00:17:55,790 --> 00:17:56,590
By the way,

281
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:58,070
how is Liu Chu

282
00:17:58,830 --> 00:18:00,200
treating you now?

283
00:18:03,750 --> 00:18:05,400
Liu Chu has changed, too.

284
00:18:08,030 --> 00:18:10,000
I really hope the next plan

285
00:18:10,000 --> 00:18:11,400
can be implemented soon.

286
00:18:12,440 --> 00:18:13,680
What plan?

287
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:16,240
Nothing.

288
00:18:17,640 --> 00:18:19,750
Look at your big belly.

289
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:21,680
If I were Liu Chu,

290
00:18:21,680 --> 00:18:23,540
I wouldn't come to see you either.

291
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:25,170
What are you talking about?

292
00:18:26,030 --> 00:18:27,830
I am pregnant with his child.

293
00:18:29,160 --> 00:18:30,160
Okay. Okay. Okay.

294
00:18:30,310 --> 00:18:31,480
I was just kidding.

295
00:18:32,030 --> 00:18:33,880
Liu Chu just recovered from his illness

296
00:18:33,880 --> 00:18:36,240
and encountered
the Eldest Princess's rebellion,

297
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:38,970
it's understandable that
he hasn't visited you.

298
00:18:41,830 --> 00:18:42,680
Your Majesty.

299
00:18:43,030 --> 00:18:44,110
Two of the three Chief Ministers of

300
00:18:44,110 --> 00:18:46,030
Jinglan have died.

301
00:18:46,480 --> 00:18:48,350
And the other one has been infected
with Gu poison.

302
00:18:48,350 --> 00:18:49,680
Eldest Princess Liu Xie

303
00:18:49,680 --> 00:18:50,790
was imprisoned by Liu Chu

304
00:18:50,790 --> 00:18:52,030
for rebelling.

305
00:18:52,480 --> 00:18:53,790
What about the spies we sent?

306
00:18:53,790 --> 00:18:55,350
Jin Xi has returned to the Princess

307
00:18:55,350 --> 00:18:57,010
to continue spying on Liu Chu.

308
00:18:58,160 --> 00:18:59,200
Fei Zheng

309
00:18:59,200 --> 00:19:00,680
was poisoned by Gu poison

310
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:02,200
at my mercy.

311
00:19:10,160 --> 00:19:11,240
Your health...

312
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:14,830
I am fine.

313
00:19:15,000 --> 00:19:16,160
I feel great.

314
00:19:16,240 --> 00:19:17,830
I will live to see the day

315
00:19:17,830 --> 00:19:19,550
we defeat Jinglan

316
00:19:19,550 --> 00:19:21,270
and capture Liu Chu.

317
00:19:23,830 --> 00:19:25,830
Gan Yi is training the troops every day.

318
00:19:25,830 --> 00:19:27,430
The army is ready for battle.

319
00:19:27,880 --> 00:19:29,410
You are wise, Your majesty.

320
00:19:29,480 --> 00:19:30,440
Where is Han Lie?

321
00:19:31,640 --> 00:19:33,590
He is developing a new Gu poison.

322
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:36,200
It will be spread all over Jinglan.

323
00:19:40,590 --> 00:19:41,590
Good.

324
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:43,640
Excellent.

325
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:55,070
His Majesty has arrived.

326
00:19:55,070 --> 00:19:57,880
Your Highness, receive His Majesty.

327
00:20:10,270 --> 00:20:11,070
Coward.

328
00:20:12,590 --> 00:20:14,350
What's the point of locking me up here?

329
00:20:14,350 --> 00:20:15,640
If you want to kill me,

330
00:20:16,160 --> 00:20:17,160
make it quick.

331
00:20:17,350 --> 00:20:18,240
Xie.

332
00:20:18,640 --> 00:20:19,920
Everyone says

333
00:20:20,680 --> 00:20:22,280
we are the closest siblings.

334
00:20:22,750 --> 00:20:24,000
If I kill you,

335
00:20:24,830 --> 00:20:26,430
they will call me heartless.

336
00:20:28,680 --> 00:20:29,590
Closest?

337
00:20:30,400 --> 00:20:32,110
How long ago was that?

338
00:20:32,590 --> 00:20:34,850
You were the late Emperor's first child.

339
00:20:35,160 --> 00:20:36,030
Our father

340
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:39,160
raised you as an emperor.

341
00:20:39,440 --> 00:20:40,880
You mastered

342
00:20:40,880 --> 00:20:41,880
both literary

343
00:20:41,880 --> 00:20:43,080
and military skills.

344
00:20:43,790 --> 00:20:45,000
In reading people

345
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:46,060
and managing them,

346
00:20:46,270 --> 00:20:47,870
you were also superior to me.

347
00:20:48,880 --> 00:20:49,790
I admit it.

348
00:20:50,240 --> 00:20:52,840
You were the child our father
was most proud of.

349
00:20:53,400 --> 00:20:54,480
If you were a man,

350
00:20:55,160 --> 00:20:57,820
I would have had no chance
to succeed the throne.

351
00:21:08,070 --> 00:21:09,030
Father.

352
00:21:10,350 --> 00:21:11,590
Father.

353
00:21:13,070 --> 00:21:15,790
Why did you teach me the art of ruling?

354
00:21:16,590 --> 00:21:19,190
Why did you give me
the abilities of an emperor?

355
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:21,750
Why didn't you raise me

356
00:21:21,750 --> 00:21:23,680
like an ordinary princess?

357
00:21:26,790 --> 00:21:29,350
Why did you treat me like this?

358
00:21:30,750 --> 00:21:32,200
Why on earth?

359
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:33,640
Why?

360
00:21:34,350 --> 00:21:36,030
This may be our fate.

361
00:21:37,030 --> 00:21:38,070
Xie.

362
00:21:38,680 --> 00:21:39,270
Fate?

363
00:21:40,400 --> 00:21:41,640
I am the Eldest Princess.

364
00:21:41,640 --> 00:21:42,880
My fate should be

365
00:21:42,880 --> 00:21:44,030
in my own hands.

366
00:21:44,400 --> 00:21:45,590
What are you?

367
00:21:45,590 --> 00:21:47,270
Do you even deserve to be an emperor?

368
00:21:47,270 --> 00:21:48,670
Can you manage the court?

369
00:21:49,160 --> 00:21:50,750
Can you defend against foreign enemies?

370
00:21:50,750 --> 00:21:52,480
Can you control the officials?

371
00:21:53,680 --> 00:21:54,550
I am telling you,

372
00:21:54,550 --> 00:21:55,640
Jinglan

373
00:21:55,960 --> 00:21:58,220
will be destroyed by you sooner or later.

374
00:22:00,240 --> 00:22:01,550
Rest assured, Xie.

375
00:22:04,750 --> 00:22:05,950
Drink this cup of wine

376
00:22:07,030 --> 00:22:09,160
and watch over me from heaven.

377
00:22:10,350 --> 00:22:11,680
For everything you worry about

378
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:12,680
and doubt,

379
00:22:13,350 --> 00:22:14,880
I will prove to you one by one
that I am right.

380
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:15,610
What's more,

381
00:22:16,400 --> 00:22:18,530
I will deal with everything very well.

382
00:22:27,510 --> 00:22:28,590
After I drink it,

383
00:22:30,880 --> 00:22:32,680
you can announce

384
00:22:35,000 --> 00:22:36,350
that I died of illness.

385
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:40,090
I will use the highest imperial honors

386
00:22:41,160 --> 00:22:43,270
to give you a grand burial.

387
00:22:44,550 --> 00:22:45,440
To me,

388
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:48,350
you will always be like our mother,

389
00:22:49,960 --> 00:22:50,880
Xie.

390
00:23:12,480 --> 00:23:13,480
Liu Chu.

391
00:23:14,350 --> 00:23:15,480
I hope

392
00:23:17,000 --> 00:23:19,160
you can keep your word.

393
00:23:52,400 --> 00:23:53,200
Father,

394
00:23:56,750 --> 00:23:57,550
I am coming.

395
00:24:22,590 --> 00:24:23,590
Oh, you.

396
00:24:24,310 --> 00:24:25,640
You are the emperor now,

397
00:24:25,680 --> 00:24:27,350
but you still let me do this for you?

398
00:24:27,350 --> 00:24:28,960
I can't trust anyone else.

399
00:24:29,350 --> 00:24:30,200
Besides,

400
00:24:30,440 --> 00:24:31,310
no one has

401
00:24:31,310 --> 00:24:32,750
skills as good as yours.

402
00:24:32,790 --> 00:24:33,680
Okay.

403
00:24:34,000 --> 00:24:35,830
Just lie here quietly

404
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:37,010
and don't bother me.

405
00:24:39,240 --> 00:24:40,830
I will always be with you

406
00:24:41,070 --> 00:24:42,550
and assist you.

407
00:24:43,030 --> 00:24:44,070
I believe

408
00:24:44,350 --> 00:24:46,750
you will definitely revitalize the court,

409
00:24:47,270 --> 00:24:48,930
bring honor to the Liu family,

410
00:24:49,640 --> 00:24:51,440
and restore our father's glory.

411
00:24:52,030 --> 00:24:56,240
By the mandate of Heaven,
the Emperor decrees:

412
00:24:56,510 --> 00:24:58,640
the Eldest Princess, Liu Xie,

413
00:24:58,960 --> 00:25:00,790
contracted a severe illness

414
00:25:00,790 --> 00:25:02,790
and passed away suddenly.

415
00:25:03,310 --> 00:25:05,750
As my flesh and blood,

416
00:25:06,270 --> 00:25:09,640
she will be buried with imperial honors.

417
00:25:09,920 --> 00:25:11,880
Her coffin will be kept for seven days

418
00:25:11,880 --> 00:25:17,000
before burial in the imperial
mausoleum. By Imperial Command.

419
00:25:19,400 --> 00:25:21,480
Just bless me well from heaven.

420
00:25:22,030 --> 00:25:24,400
All your worries and doubts,

421
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:26,160
I will show you one by one.

422
00:25:26,160 --> 00:25:26,890
What's more,

423
00:25:27,270 --> 00:25:28,750
I will do it very well.

424
00:25:43,440 --> 00:25:45,750
Why did you ask me to meet you
during the day?

425
00:25:45,750 --> 00:25:46,510
Don't worry.

426
00:25:47,070 --> 00:25:47,930
I'm the only one

427
00:25:48,590 --> 00:25:49,790
who will come here.

428
00:25:50,680 --> 00:25:52,000
No one else will see us.

429
00:25:52,750 --> 00:25:54,270
She temporarily went back to Changmo

430
00:25:54,270 --> 00:25:55,880
and didn't leave the antidote.

431
00:25:55,880 --> 00:25:57,510
So, your Gu poison might...

432
00:25:58,640 --> 00:26:00,030
That's good.

433
00:26:00,350 --> 00:26:02,830
Rather than being a killing tool,

434
00:26:04,270 --> 00:26:06,070
it's better to die a quick death.

435
00:26:08,480 --> 00:26:10,410
Are you really not afraid of death?

436
00:26:10,640 --> 00:26:11,440
Death?

437
00:26:15,750 --> 00:26:16,960
As spies,

438
00:26:17,270 --> 00:26:18,350
shouldn't we have

439
00:26:18,350 --> 00:26:20,350
put life aside long ago?

440
00:26:24,480 --> 00:26:25,270
Have a seat.

441
00:26:31,350 --> 00:26:32,810
Before coming to Jinglan,

442
00:26:33,030 --> 00:26:34,090
I was just like you.

443
00:26:34,880 --> 00:26:35,720
I thought

444
00:26:35,720 --> 00:26:36,880
that dying for Changmo

445
00:26:36,880 --> 00:26:38,410
was a very honorable thing.

446
00:26:39,350 --> 00:26:40,720
At that time, I only cared about

447
00:26:40,720 --> 00:26:42,790
the missions assigned by Changmo.

448
00:26:43,880 --> 00:26:46,010
I remember the first time I saw Liu Chu.

449
00:26:46,480 --> 00:26:48,400
I wanted to kill him right away.

450
00:26:50,200 --> 00:26:51,240
Unfortunately,

451
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:54,640
my mission at that time
was to stay in the Prince's Mansion

452
00:26:54,640 --> 00:26:55,770
and stay by his side.

453
00:27:00,400 --> 00:27:02,960
Later, Xiao Chi also entered
the Prince's Mansion.

454
00:27:02,960 --> 00:27:05,960
They dragged me to mess around,

455
00:27:06,270 --> 00:27:08,670
turning the Prince's Mansion upside down.

456
00:27:09,030 --> 00:27:10,750
I thought they were very silly

457
00:27:11,270 --> 00:27:12,240
and childish.

458
00:27:23,480 --> 00:27:24,550
Then,

459
00:27:25,480 --> 00:27:26,480
somehow,

460
00:27:26,960 --> 00:27:28,400
I became like them,

461
00:27:29,350 --> 00:27:31,070
going behind the manager's back

462
00:27:31,070 --> 00:27:32,870
and sneaking out of the mansion.

463
00:27:33,640 --> 00:27:35,170
At that time, the three of us

464
00:27:36,030 --> 00:27:36,960
were teenagers

465
00:27:37,480 --> 00:27:40,010
and dared to fight for justice
on the streets.

466
00:27:40,240 --> 00:27:43,500
Every day, we were chased
and beaten by dozens of ruffians.

467
00:27:44,030 --> 00:27:45,160
Once

468
00:27:45,310 --> 00:27:46,640
we got into big trouble,

469
00:27:47,200 --> 00:27:49,130
I took a beating for the two of them.

470
00:27:49,270 --> 00:27:50,880
They cried right next to me.

471
00:27:54,240 --> 00:27:55,300
Hearing their cry,

472
00:28:05,030 --> 00:28:05,960
for the first time in my life,

473
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:07,830
I felt a warmth in my heart.

474
00:28:15,440 --> 00:28:16,240
Jin Xi,

475
00:28:18,400 --> 00:28:20,860
if someone is willing
to take risks with you,

476
00:28:22,030 --> 00:28:23,200
get into trouble,

477
00:28:23,680 --> 00:28:25,140
and take responsibility,

478
00:28:27,110 --> 00:28:28,790
it's a happy thing.

479
00:28:41,880 --> 00:28:42,640
I really hope

480
00:28:43,880 --> 00:28:45,680
you'll feel the same way I do.

481
00:29:21,030 --> 00:29:22,000
Greetings, Your Majesty.

482
00:29:22,000 --> 00:29:23,000
You are pregnant.

483
00:29:23,640 --> 00:29:24,900
There is no need to bow.

484
00:29:25,240 --> 00:29:26,640
I had nothing to do,

485
00:29:26,680 --> 00:29:28,030
so I came to see you.

486
00:29:29,350 --> 00:29:30,550
Consort Ling,

487
00:29:30,550 --> 00:29:31,880
are you homesick again?

488
00:29:33,750 --> 00:29:34,550
No.

489
00:29:35,640 --> 00:29:37,770
Changmo sent many tributes recently.

490
00:29:37,960 --> 00:29:38,920
If you miss home,

491
00:29:39,400 --> 00:29:40,800
open them and take a look.

492
00:29:40,960 --> 00:29:43,030
I will send you some more maids

493
00:29:43,350 --> 00:29:45,030
to keep you company.

494
00:29:47,310 --> 00:29:48,970
I have been a bit tired lately.

495
00:29:49,880 --> 00:29:51,880
And I don't have much time
to spend with you.

496
00:29:51,880 --> 00:29:52,510
Why don't

497
00:29:53,240 --> 00:29:53,750
you stay in

498
00:29:53,750 --> 00:29:55,810
the Consort Ling Pavilion I gave you?

499
00:29:56,350 --> 00:29:57,610
Don't come out for now.

500
00:29:58,000 --> 00:29:59,200
Take care of our baby.

501
00:30:03,030 --> 00:30:03,680
Go back.

502
00:30:06,640 --> 00:30:08,300
Be careful not to catch a cold.

503
00:30:15,550 --> 00:30:16,240
Guards!

504
00:30:16,720 --> 00:30:17,440
Yes.

505
00:30:19,640 --> 00:30:21,640
Summon Fei Zheng and Xiao Chi
to see me.

506
00:30:21,640 --> 00:30:22,270
Also,

507
00:30:23,880 --> 00:30:26,070
tell the Imperial Guard
not to sleep tonight.

508
00:30:26,070 --> 00:30:27,730
Have them ready for my orders.

509
00:30:28,030 --> 00:30:29,000
Yes.

510
00:31:11,640 --> 00:31:12,480
Are you okay?

511
00:31:13,590 --> 00:31:14,270
Didn't I tell you

512
00:31:14,270 --> 00:31:16,000
not to come in without my order?

513
00:31:17,160 --> 00:31:17,960
His Majesty has issued a decree

514
00:31:17,960 --> 00:31:18,790
ordering you to enter the palace now.

515
00:31:18,790 --> 00:31:19,640
Got it.

516
00:31:20,030 --> 00:31:20,790
Get out.

517
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:21,640
Yes.

518
00:31:51,270 --> 00:31:52,070
Your Majesty,

519
00:31:53,310 --> 00:31:54,200
I'm late.

520
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:57,370
Apologies for making you wait.

521
00:31:57,830 --> 00:31:59,000
Xiao Chi and I

522
00:31:59,240 --> 00:32:00,770
have already started a pot.

523
00:32:00,880 --> 00:32:01,720
You

524
00:32:02,310 --> 00:32:03,270
should drink as a penalty.

525
00:32:03,270 --> 00:32:04,070
I

526
00:32:04,070 --> 00:32:05,270
will drink three cups as a penalty.

527
00:32:05,270 --> 00:32:06,470
Among the three of us,

528
00:32:06,480 --> 00:32:08,080
you have the best tolerance.

529
00:32:08,640 --> 00:32:10,030
Instead of three cups,

530
00:32:11,590 --> 00:32:12,790
how about three pots?

531
00:32:13,750 --> 00:32:14,310
I will

532
00:32:15,110 --> 00:32:16,770
obey Your Majesty's command.

533
00:32:18,480 --> 00:32:19,880
The three of us

534
00:32:19,880 --> 00:32:21,030
haven't seen

535
00:32:21,270 --> 00:32:23,240
much of each other over the years.

536
00:32:23,750 --> 00:32:24,790
Tonight,

537
00:32:24,790 --> 00:32:26,030
we have such fine wine.

538
00:32:26,030 --> 00:32:27,090
How can we waste it?

539
00:32:27,200 --> 00:32:27,640
Come,

540
00:32:27,880 --> 00:32:28,940
let's have a toast.

541
00:32:30,750 --> 00:32:31,550
Well,

542
00:32:31,790 --> 00:32:32,390
Fei Zheng,

543
00:32:33,590 --> 00:32:34,960
you'd drink a whole pot.

544
00:32:40,680 --> 00:32:41,750
Look at my memory.

545
00:32:42,350 --> 00:32:43,680
The penalty is three pots.

546
00:32:43,680 --> 00:32:44,400
Three pots.

547
00:32:45,270 --> 00:32:47,200
Now that Zheng is so straightforward,

548
00:32:47,200 --> 00:32:48,660
I should keep him company.

549
00:32:49,030 --> 00:32:49,880
Are you sure?

550
00:32:51,350 --> 00:32:52,160
Of course.

551
00:32:55,720 --> 00:32:56,480
Good.

552
00:32:56,750 --> 00:32:57,810
Straightforward.

553
00:32:58,590 --> 00:32:59,590
Then let's drink.

554
00:33:00,160 --> 00:33:00,960
Today,

555
00:33:01,200 --> 00:33:02,550
let’s

556
00:33:02,550 --> 00:33:03,640
drink till we drop.
